OL,3,CFootball fan banned after mocking
OL,4,CMunich air disaster
OL,6,FA football fan has been banned from
OL,7,Fattending matches for three years
OL,8,Fafter mocking the Munich air disaster.
OL,10,Fsupporter Mark Finnigan was at
OL,11,Ffootball stadium watching his club
OL,12,Fface on 9 March 2024.
OL,14,FAfter the reds were awarded a penalty,
OL,15,Fthe 24-year-old was seen by police
OL,16,Fmaking "a hand gesture...related to
OL,17,Fthe Munich air disaster" towards the
OL,18,Fhome crowd.
