OL,3,CFootball fan banned after mocking
OL,4,CMunich air disaster
OL,6,F23 people, including eight Manchester
OL,7,FUnited players and three members of
OL,8,Fclub staff, were killed in the on 6
OL,9,FFebruary 1958.
OL,11,FFinnigan was removed from the crowd
OL,12,Fand arrested on suspicion of using
OL,13,Fthreatening or abusive words or
OL,14,Fbehaviour with intent to cause
OL,15,Fharassment, alarm, or distress.
OL,17,FHe admitted the gesture "could be
OL,18,Finterpreted as being related to the
OL,19,FMunich air disaster" and pleaded
OL,20,Fguilty on Wednesday 10 April.
