OL,6,FAs well as receiving a three-year ban
OL,7,Ffrom all matches, he was also handed a
OL,8,Fsix month conditional discharge -
OL,9,Fwhich could result in a harsher
OL,10,Fsentence should he ignore the ban.
OL,12,FDave Lewis, Everton's Head of Security
OL,13,Fand Stadium Safety Officer, said: "We
OL,14,Fhave a clear and well-publicised zero-
OL,15,Ftolerance policy on all forms of
OL,16,Fdiscrimination and that includes
OL,17,Fchanting or actions related to
OL,18,Ftragedies.
